ctrl + b + % - horizontal split
ctrl + b + " - vertical split
ctrl + b + l - move editor to the right
ctrl + b + h - move editor to the left
ctrl + b + j - move editor to the down
ctrl + b + k - move editor to the up
ctrl + b + t - open new terminal
ctrl + b + c - open new file
ctrl + n - move to the next tab (editor)
ctrl + p - move to the previous tab (editor)
ctrl + e - files explorer search
ctrl + shift + e - move to the files explorer and back
ctrl + shift + f - move to the global search
